number\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\n                    Ζωπύρου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φαινώ\">ΦΑΙΝΟΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ζωπύρης\">ΖΩΠΥΡΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φαινώ\">ΦΑΙΝΟΙ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ζωπύρης\">ΖΩΠΥΡΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":221,"html":222},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001159_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001159_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001159.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001159-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":224,"html":225},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":227,"html":228},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Phaino, of Zopyros, goodbye!\u003C/p>  ",{"id":230,"html":231},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The simple use of the genitive for Zopyros means that we cannot tell whether Phaino is his wife or daughter. Given, however, the similarities with \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001160\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001160\u003C/a>, it is likely that this is the same man, therefore we can reconstruct his name as Zopyros son of Artemon. There are half a dozen other mentions of the name Zopyros in Sicily and it is quite common elsewhere, whereas Phanoi is rarer, appearing in an inscription from Athens (CIG. I.1013).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":233,"html":234},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>  \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">340.1\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 1974 11 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001397\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001397\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":236,"html":237},"handnote"," \u003Cp>Letters are extremely regular and neat, with letter heights all identical (except for phi in line 1, which extends above the guideline). Letters are thin, tall and evenly spaced. Terminal dots carved on all letters. Use of the classic zeta in line 2.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  39 (phi in line 1: 49mm)  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":239,"html":240},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[242,244,247,249,252,253,256,257],{"html":243},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Alex Antoniou",{"id":245,"lang":125,"html":246},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\n                    Ζωπύρου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φαινώ\">Φαινοῖ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ζωπύρης\">Ζωπύρου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":248},"Text encoding: Victoria Fendel",{"id":250,"html":251},"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Φαινοῖ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Φαινώ\">Φαινοῖ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Ζωπύρου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ζωπύρης\">Ζωπύρου\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":243},{"id":254,"lang":125,"html":255},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-